					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Please note that I only suggested it to John when I met him at an event. He said that it would have to up to the SNES programmer to see if he was interested in releasing/selling his tools. <br /><br />Since NESmaker was so successful. It seems as if it would only make sense if they also did a kickstarter and did some sort of SNES maker tool.</div>

