					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">I think the key lesson is...if you want a COMMERCIALLY successful SNES game, it should have multiple layers (parallax), or Mario Kart style perspective, or professional quality artwork.<br /><br />But, freeware homebrews, should be free to look like Space Invaders to be &quot;good&quot; (see Classic Kong).</div>

					
						<div class="postbody"><br />_________________<br /><a href="http://nesdoug.com" class="postlink">nesdoug.com</a> -- blog/tutorial on programming for the NES</div>
