				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Thing is, if I see a homebrew severely underutilizing the platform it was coded for, I'll hardly be interested. When someone targets a specific console, I expect them to use most of the features it has to offer, and I expect the game to look AT LEAST like the typical games made for that system back in the day (If they go the extra mile and try to surpass what the typical games had to offer, even better!), otherwise I'll feel underwhelmed.</div>

